text.paragraph:
Administration of adequate amounts of fluid with the capsule formulation of tetracycline is recommended to wash down the drug and reduce the risk of esophageal irritation and ulceration (see 
                        ADVERSE REACTIONS
                     ).

In patients with renal impairment (see 
                        WARNINGS
                     ): decrease total dosage by reduction of recommended individual doses and/or by extending time intervals between doses.
